* Live Email Finisher Notifications. Automated Email Alerts for Finishers.
*   When to use:    Run this live during the race to send instant notifications as participants cross the finish line.
*   How to use:     Ensure the EMAIL field in your database contains valid email addresses. Double-click to start the listener;
*                   an email is triggered each time a new finish time is recorded.
*   Setup:          Configure SendGrid API key and sender in Entries.INI (%email_apikey%, %email_from%).
Announce            Headers
Announce Event      Finish

* Message Construction
Message             Congrats
Space               1
Field               First Name
Squeeze
Space               0
Message             , you've finished the %race name%.
Line Feed
Message             Official Results: https://results.raceroster.com/v3/events/%resultsid5k%/

/* Recommendation: Avoid including the finish time directly in the email.
Times can change due to manual corrections or chip-to-gun adjustments.
Providing a results URL is the most accurate way to share data.
*/

* Optional Time Formatting (Commented Out)
* Field             RACE
* Message           event, in a time of
* Event             Finish
* Minus             ChipStart
* Time Format       H:MM:SS.01

EMAIL TO            EMAIL
Email Subject       %email_subject% - You've Finished!
EMAIL SERVER        sendgrid
EMAIL APIKEY        %email_apikey%
EMAIL FROM          %email_from%
